         <abstract>
            <p>This article summarizes 30 years of investment management history and provides some vision of the future. The investment management industry has evolved from the dark age of the past to the information age of today. Tomorrow, the investment industry will consist of investment factories and small boutiques. The pension sponsor mantra of the future will reflect the basic economic principal of value for service from money managers and consultants.</p>
          </abstract>
